&nbsp;<br />
The President and many in Congress decided that we&rsquo;re going to do them here. &nbsp;We&rsquo;re going to build these plants -- construct these plants in America. &nbsp;We&rsquo;re going to build these products in America. &nbsp;We&rsquo;re going to employ Americans. &nbsp;And I think that&rsquo;s a strong economic record.<br />
