Q Thank you. &nbsp;Robert, do you believe that Americans associate the Clinton era, the Clinton presidency with a time of more economic bounty or better economic opportunity for America? And aside from all the Chamber questions, et cetera, does the administration want to send a signal to Americans that you&rsquo;re tapping President Clinton&rsquo;s expertise, people like Jack Lew, in an effort to bring some of that back? &nbsp;Or do you think that that's --<br />
